Package: anglr
Type: Package
Title: Mesh Topology for Spatial Data
Version: 0.4.4
Authors@R: c(person("Michael D.","Sumner", role = c("aut", "cre"), email ="mdsumner@gmail.com"), 
             person("Miles", "McBain", role = c("ctb")))
Description: Helpers for creating meshes from geographical spatial data and 
 translating data formats into forms ready for mesh visualization with 'OpenGL' 
 (the Open Graphics Library <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenGL>) via the 'rgl'
 package. This package extends the classes defined in the 'silicate' package 
 adding high-quality triangulations suitable for surface representation and 
 providing methods for 3D plots for a wide range of spatial data sources. 
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0),  silicate (>= 0.2.0)
